  "description": "This individual is a human undead, preserved by the desiccating winds and mineral ash of the fissure, with taupe skinTone drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and jaw. Brown eyes sit recessed beneath a heavy brow, and brown hair lies in long, dirt-matted lengths that frame a gaunt, leathery face. The mouthline is fixed in a permanent rictus from dried tissue loss, and the hands show rigid fingers with blackened nail beds typical of long exposure to caustic grit. Their bearing is rigid and deliberate, reflecting the compulsive endurance of the dead bound to place and routine.",
